    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1865-05-29T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1865-05-29T00:00:00-05:00" n="658" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d658">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Hunter</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                                Tassara</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>,</placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1865-05-29">
                            <hi rend="italic">May</hi> 29, 1865.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The undersigned, Acting Secretary of State, has the honor to acknowledge
                            the receipt of Mr. Tassara’s note of the 22d instant, relative to the
                            arrival at Havana of the insurgent ram Stonewall; and to offer to him on
                            this occasion renewed assurances of his very high consideration.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>W. HUNTER.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Señor Don <hi rend="smallcaps">Gabriel Garcia y Tassara</hi>, <hi rend="italic">&amp;c., &amp;c., Washington.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
